                  , on the King's highway, putting him in corporal fear and danger of his life, and taking from him one basket, value 2 d. one cloth, value 2 d. and three geese, the property of <rs id="t17820109-6-viclabel30" type="occupation">Messrs.</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820109-6-victim104 t17820109-6-viclabel30"></join>
